# Be Civic project marker.
#
# The be-civic plugin's gate skill checks for this file (or one in a parent
# directory) to detect that the conversation is running inside a Be Civic
# project. When present, the project's CLAUDE.md harness is treated as the
# active session context and the gate skill exits quietly.
#
# All Be Civic system state — sessions, observation buffers, pending submissions
# — lives under this .be-civic/ directory. User-visible state (profile.json,
# MEMORY.md, documents/, research notes) lives at the project root.
#
# Do not delete this file unless you want to convert the folder back to a
# non-Be-Civic folder.
